en.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Thanh-T%C3%A2m-t%C3%A0i-nh%C3%A2n/M%E1%BB%99ng-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1m-Ti%C3%AAn-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-t%E1%BB%AB-th%E1%BA%ADp-th%E1%BB%A7-k%E1%BB%B3-10-Kh%E1%BB%91c-t%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-t%C6%B0/poem-GcCrhlJwT-z6e0P-U7pBLg">Mộng Đạm Tiên đề từ thập thủ kỳ 10 - Khốc tương tư - 夢淡仙題詞十首其十－哭相思</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Thanh-T%C3%A2m-t%C3%A0i-nh%C3%A2n/author-Ry0GXj_uifS6AejvZUIukQ">Thanh Tâm tài nhân</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/M%E1%BA%A1c-%C4%90%C4%A9nh-Chi/Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-t%E1%BB%89nh-li%C3%AAn-ph%C3%BA/poem-kmc4IXweJeTsqjRgFM3A6A">Ngọc tỉnh liên phú - 玉井蓮賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/M%E1%BA%A1c-%C4%90%C4%A9nh-Chi/author-7dFsTrXHz60sugbdOHPrjQ">Mạc Đĩnh Chi</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%97-T%E1%BA%A5n/T%E1%BA%B7ng-%E1%BB%94-K%E1%BB%B3-S%C6%A1n/poem-EmFk763AusXIuN6FmhqAvw">Tặng Ổ Kỳ Sơn - 贈鄔其山</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%97-T%E1%BA%A5n/author-TXAaCmjdRWIV6MkCYE1psQ">Lỗ Tấn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/V%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%81/poem-aGvPEymxVFhXwpQtyOd-DQ">Vô đề - 無題</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br></div>	</div>
